import { useForm } from "react-hook-form" const Popup=({open,data})=>{ const{register,handleSubmit,formState:{errors,isDirty,dirtyFields},watch}=useForm({defaultValues:data}) const submitForm=(data)=>{ console.log(isDirty) } const formData=watch() const isChanged=JSON.stringify(formData)!=JSON.stringify(data) console.log(isDirty,isChanged) return( <>
) } export default Popup;
